id=onyx-camera-fix
name=Redmi Turbo 4 Pro Dual-Camera Fix
version=v1.0
versionCode=1
author=Samiul Basir Fahim
description=Systemlessly restores camera operation on Global/India ROMs. Fixes broken hardware mapping caused by non-CN firmware omitting drivers for specific Turbo 4 Pro hardware sensor batches. Injects missing vendor drivers (_ii blobs) and patches SELinux constraints.
